data.description:
Welcome to this adorable 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home with a private setting on wooded ¾ of an acre, with easy access to downtown, Clinton Highway, Cedar Bluff and much more!  BRAND NEW HVAC. 

This move-in ready home features 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms in a cozy layout!

The entire home features a modern luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout with no carpet at all! The spacious living room has great natural light with a well-done shiplap accent wall, featuring a handy shoe compartment that can be utilized as an entry way table or tv stand! 

The open layout includes a view to the dining space which has been equipped with a custom hand-made dining room table, large enough to fit 6 people. 
Check out the seating storage as well! 

The kitchen has been beautifully updated with a clean, subway tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances (that convey, including the washer and dryer) white cabinetry, with modern black hardware.

Next to the kitchen you will find a newly installed pantry area and/or coffee bar, with a stackable, new washer and dryer.



The hallway bathroom includes a beautiful furniture storage piece over the toilet, with a shiplap accent wall and modern but antique vanity. 

The spacious primary suite, large enough for a king bed and additional furniture, includes a spacious walk-in closet, and en-suite bathroom with shower/tub combo. 

The 2nd bedroom includes a custom shiplap accent wall, also spacious enough for a king bed with additional furniture! 

The 3rd bedroom could be utilized as either a bedroom or office space with great natural light. 

Enjoy the privacy on your large back deck, complete with a pergola and gate for children or pets. 
The backyard is incredibly spacious sitting on just under an acre of land! Walk on over to a huge fire pit large enough to host all your gatherings and parties! 

Enjoy an abundant supply of firewood which has been stacked to perfection! 

Need storage? Check out the bottom half of the home with features a walk-in basement, with electrical. Plenty of space to store holiday items, toys or anything else your heart desires!

Want a garage? There's a perfect spot as you pull in on the left of the house, perfect for a two car garage one day! 
Let's not forget proximity to everything nearby! 
Less than 5 mins to Walmart neighborhood market. 2 gyms nearby! 
Clinton Hwy less than 10 minutes. University of Tennessee and downtown less than 12! 

Come see this charming property today!
